{"tid":1622370,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【出街前必set】【不要被自殺/失蹤】2","createTime":"2019-10-04T16:05:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T02:18:31.000Z","uid":272569,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a59cadc2083574503ac0331c9825b0370e032fb0","tid":1622370,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:05:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins>唔好用touch id 或 face id, <br />\n密碼set 4/6 pin, 最好6pin無咁易中</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><strong>0-鎖sim 同whatsapp設定</strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">[入link幫手推] 全民盡快鎖返張sim card<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1621024\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1621024</a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n［重要］黑警用SIM卡入手足WhatsApp!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1617741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1617741</a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><strong>1-裝parachute</strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">[替代fb live] 發夢App試用後感（只限IOS）- Parachute<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1398220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1398220</a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></blockquote><br />\nApp Store: <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/parachute/id999134752?l=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fparachute%2Fid999134752%3Fl%3Den&d=tg2x2Vtgsuxlq6ErvfvNjoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=8979a1cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/parachute/id999134752?l=en</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2-Telegram set schedule message</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n最好每次出街出門口前都set, 唔一定要夢遊前，特別係比狗抄過牌嘅，或做緊其它嘢嘅<br />\n因為試過有手足出門口都比狗逗，所以萬事小心<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Telegram呢個功能隨時救你一命<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1573682\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1573682</a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><ins>4-裝VPN, 個人用緊Nord VPN</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">買NordVPN<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1618990\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1618990</a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></blockquote><br />\n另外 <span style=\"color: blue;\">身體誠實</span> 巴打整在個參考<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1LPgDYHLaeMHCjpfkFucInIPq3oVrh-7XuTClJzCaubU/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1LPgDYHLaeMHCjpfkFucInIPq3oVrh-7XuTClJzCaubU%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=tg2x2Vtgsuxlq6ErvfvNjoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=333cc2e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1LPgDYHLaeMHCjpfkFucInIPq3oVrh-7XuTClJzCaubU/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n</span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins>5-留DNA, 如果你信得過個記者先好搵佢, 但個人覺得留DNA都唔錯</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">【招訪問】有位法新社記者想訪問收集左自己DNA嘅前線!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1601256\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1601256</a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins>＊＊＊＊＊5 Telegram Tools＊＊＊＊＊</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"> <ins><em><strong>i) 查校巴 </strong></em></ins>(發緊夢時都可以用，行過見到可疑車可以㩒兩下，可能會搵到稀有道具，好似汽油咁）￼<br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://t.me/hkaeb_car_plate_check_bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkaeb_car_plate_check_bot&d=tg2x2Vtgsuxlq6ErvfvNjoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=2a50e1b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkaeb_car_plate_check_bot</a></blockquote><br />\n如果過左十次又未出事可以經直接去 <blockquote><a href=\"https://t.me/fakeyeejoi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffakeyeejoi&d=tg2x2Vtgsuxlq6ErvfvNjoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=ec2c2d2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/fakeyeejoi</a></blockquote><br />\n注意上車最好棄裝，記車牌，唔好係車講發夢嘢<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>ii) 即時地圖</strong></ins>, 哨兵或前線記得抽時間睇下 <blockquote><a href=\"https://t.me/hkmapverify_bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkmapverify_bot&d=tg2x2Vtgsuxlq6ErvfvNjoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=853470db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkmapverify_bot</a></blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">HKMAP即時地圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1403678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1403678</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>iii) 查大廈密碼：</strong></ins><blockquote><a href=\"https://t.me/checkbuildingpw_bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcheckbuildingpw_bot&d=tg2x2Vtgsuxlq6ErvfvNjoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=d181d718\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/checkbuildingpw_bot</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n另外restart-hk 都有好多資料, 都可以去佢地channel睇睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Restart_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FRestart_HK&d=tg2x2Vtgsuxlq6ErvfvNjoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=221e4b89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Restart_HK</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><em>祝各位武運瘋狂</em></em></strong>"},{"pid":"af784e2ae822d52f77e06bd27fe5d604b59a7d76","tid":1622370,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:13:19.000Z","msg":"VPN 唔好用免費嘢<br />\n<br />\n中共控制VPN品牌一覽<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299387\" data-auto-link t